<ul>
  <li><a href="../manage-data/manage-assets.html">Notebook locking</a></li>
  <li><a href="notebook-environments.html">Use default CPU environments</a></li>
  <li><a href="spark-envs.html">Use Spark environments</a></li>
  <li><a href="manage-envs.html">Change the environment runtime used by a notebook</a></li>
</ul>

<p>See <a href="https://github.com/IBMDataScience/sample-notebooks/tree/master/CloudPakForData/notebooks">Sample notebooks</a> for additional sample notebooks.</p>


